        "system": {
          "summary": {
            "value": ""
          },
          "description": "<p>You have a <strong>lucky number</strong>; at the beginning of each session, that number is <strong>7</strong>. Once per scene after you perform a Check, you may replace the value shown on one of the dice you rolled with your lucky number (even if this would give an impossible Result, such as a value of 7 on a d6). If you do, the replaced value becomes your <strong>new</strong> lucky number.</p>",
