      {
        "name": "Stolen Time",
        "type": "skill",
        "_id": "k3y2MdKu0Y5m1mDY",
        "img": "systems/projectfu/styles/static/compendium/classes/entropist/entropist_stolen_time.png",
        "system": {
          "summary": {
            "value": ""
          },
          "description": "<p>During a conflict, you may use an action to interfere with the flow of time by spending up to <strong>【SL × 5】</strong> Mind Points. For every 5 Mind Points you spend this way, choose one option:</p><ul><li><p>One creature you can see suffers <strong>slow.</strong></p></li><li><p>One creature you can see recovers from <strong>slow.</strong></p></li><li><p>One enemy you can see that is suffering from <strong>slow</strong> loses <strong>【10 + (SL × 5)】</strong> Hit Points.</p></li><li><p>One creature you can see may perform the <strong>Equipment</strong> action for free.</p></li><li><p>Choose one ally you can see that has yet to take a turn during this round: that ally may take their turn immediately after yours during this round.</p></li></ul><p>Each option can only be chosen <strong>once</strong> per use of this Skill.</p>",
